  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      RAND/UCLA modified Delphi study on quality indicators for STEMI to determine the
      appropriateness of quality indicators retrieved from literature and guideline review. We aim
      to engage 20 cardiologists and 20 nurses with relevant experience in the care for STEMI
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
