  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>validated quality indicators for STEMI care in belgium (both on patient and on hospital level)</measure>
    <time_frame>2 months</time_frame>
    <description>33 experts in cardioloy, cardio nursing and quality rated quality indicators for STEMI care in belgian hospitals on a 9 point Likert Scale. All indicators with a median score between 7 and 9 were discussed in an expert panel. The expert panel selected validated quality inidicators for STEMI care.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
